g.text: Since the ESP8266 01 module is not stable and time to
time it stops responding, it is possible to restart
esp8266 programatically via the added relay. Simply,
when the arduino does not receive the right response,
the pin 11 is set to HIGH for several seconds which
causes that the ESP8266 is switched off for that period.
After ends of period the esp8266 is switched on
